Progressive Web Apps are not only for B2C market. We have created internal PWA for data collecting from assets. In my talk I would like to introduce into our architecture and share my experience how you can:
- integrate NFC chips with Progressive Web App; 
- use Google Apps Script as a REST API;
- store data in several databases (Firebase, Spreadsheet and Fusion Tables); 
- create dashboards, visualization (Charts API) and route planning (Maps Direction API);
